        "content": "<p><span aria-label=\"thumbs up\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44d\" role=\"img\" title=\"thumbs up\">:thumbs_up:</span> alexcrichton submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13421#pullrequestreview-4331944343\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Would this perhaps make sense to be a <code>misc</code> fuzz target? Also, could you land a change in upstream oss-fuzz passing the <code>--cfg</code> necessary before landing this?</p>\n</blockquote>",
